<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Work in progress page for Lukas Mateju's e-portfolio."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>Lukas Mateju | Work in Progress</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: #f7f7f4;
        color: #1e2933;
      }

      body {
        display: grid;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 34rem;
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        width: min(100%, 22rem);
        margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 8vw, 4rem);
        line-height: 1;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          background: #111827;
          color: #f8fafc;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Work in progress.</h1>
      <p>
        A new e-portfolio iteration is coming soon. I am rebuilding this into something a
        little cleaner, more useful, and with a lot more fun features. 
        Enjoy this picture of my dog until the new iteration is officialy live.
      </p>
      <img src="/images/photoOfPepe.jpeg" alt="Pepe" />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
